{"tid":1714407,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣] 文宣組要明白已經無得再用弱者來做文宣","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T07:49:35.000Z","uid":94771,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e82d0ca9b0250150068a4e49a15238a15cc3fcd5","tid":1714407,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:07:39.000Z","msg":"其實做開文宣組的大家都知，香港文宣暫時情況。<br />\n我地而家所謂文宣做得好唔好係<strong>基於材料</strong>，個文宣做得愈成功，<strong>人血饅頭的程度愈重</strong>。<br />\n即係我地要靠手足同路人，被人人濫捕，濫打，槍殺去做材料。<br />\n<br />\n做成一個非常唔健康的文宣狀態，我地的文宣從來無<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大力</span></strong>為同路人開脫解釋話手足行為。<br />\n<br />\n去到依個情況，文宣再用一個<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>絕對弱者</strong></span>的角度去打已經唔Work。因為手足已經會反擊，依Ｄ文宣的作用會大幅變弱。而且用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>絕對弱者</strong></span>做文宣會對某部份前線手足做成好大的錯覺，就係自我犧牲換取成個社會及外國關注。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面希望文宣唔需要再<strong>大量</strong>使用 <span style=\"color: red;\">人血饅頭</span> 去打，因為咁做會令前線同文宣脫節。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前線本土陣線愈弱，文宣愈強；前線本土陣線愈強，文宣愈弱。</span></strong>做成極之矛盾的情況。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，文宣組因為開脫上面做的力量完全唔足夠，所以無可否認已經令部份溫和人士離棄我地，而且外國的確係有轉風向批評示威者，對國際戰線其實不利。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得打後文宣，應該為手足解釋開脫同攻擊<span style=\"color: red;\">對方文宣</span>為重點。<br />\n事實上，中大無睇直播/係現場幫手的人，會覺得係學生錯，成件事的起因解釋度不足<br />\n文宣最忌覺得人地都會知咩事，而唔去解釋。比如又一城事件，大量私了事件。<br />\n<br />\n當然要注意係要了解咩事件要冷處理，咩事件要解釋<br />\n<strong>暫時要做的重大主題係 ：</strong><br />\n<ins>日本人錯被當支人私了<br />\n城巴被燒<br />\n又一城被裝修<br />\n燒電箱，交流燈<br />\n私了出現的原因<br />\n社會制度的不公<br />\n７７７無視大部份香港人</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>文宣過往因為太依賴人血饅頭，而家無可否認係轉到好弱，而因為裝修畫面鏡頭衝擊太大，令到新聞上我地係好不利。所以請大家大大力做野<br />\n</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"a262f29a8774441340af66a8b9e530bc60633629","tid":1714407,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29613d7307f3ceb5cd0b132a40936b5488dead55","tid":1714407,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a>"},{"pid":"75306956df81bc31080c6f00370bbb6141255469","tid":1714407,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe5354f5fbb020529c618f55912c9f0eac4c537","tid":1714407,"uid":135406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de85a3f7b480b261309e0e35b5bd9c3b8a8495d6","tid":1714407,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c15890334179f3a2792e4e31e9eb9d314d06c3","tid":1714407,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0c3c58d6f69783b4aee376e8653357eb75a32c","tid":1714407,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:53:23.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a9cdb6b0d778f427631489ff7ee45517ded5aa34","tid":1714407,"uid":125453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682dc07381baabcb71c0f8d47f4c98660f71df17","tid":1714407,"uid":135248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450a5b60c2b1dd64c594d3301b69ef2de9b4a2cc","tid":1714407,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-